search_results.title: Owner Gave Up on This 1967 Pontiac GTO After 50 Years ...
search_results.snippet: This 1967 Pontiac GTO spent nearly its entire life with the same owner; the car rarely hit the road, as the odo shows only 43K miles.

search_results.title: 1967 Pontiac GTO
search_results.snippet: Owner Insight: When my Dad returned from Vietnam my mom had bought him a 1966 GTO. He loved that car and would talk about it often while I was growing up.
